<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th" class="has-background-grey-darker">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bulma@0.9.3/css/bulma.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/home.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/root.css" />
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/bs.js"></script>
    <title>Workshop 9</title>
</head>

<body class="has-navbar-fixed-top">
    <nav class="navbar has-background-black-ter is-fixed-top">
        <div class="navbar-brand">
            <p class="navbar-item has-text-light">KONKAMON SION
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="navbar-start">
            <div class="navbar-item has-text-light">
                <div>
                    <p id="workshopName" class="is-hidden"><strong class="has-text-white">Workshop 9</strong> -
                        แอปพลิเคชันพยากรณ์อากาศ
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <section class="hero is-fullheight" data-bs-parallax-bg="true" id="header">
        <div class="hero-body">
            <div class="container has-text-centered">
                <p class="title has-text-white">
                    Workshop 9 - แอปพลิเคชันพยากรณ์อากาศ
                </p>
                <p class="subtitle has-text-grey-light">
                    30204-2303 การพัฒนาโปรแกรมบนอุปกรณ์เคลื่อนที่แบบพกพา
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <div class="container has-text-light">
        <div class="box has-background-black-ter content has-text-centered">
            <h1 class="has-text-light">พยากรณ์อากาศ</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="tile is-ancestor">
            <div class="tile is-parent is-justify-content-space-between">
                <div class="tile is-child box is-5 has-background-black-ter has-text-light content">
                    <h2 class="has-text-light">จากชื่อจังหวัดหรืออำเภอ</h2>
                    <hr>
                    <form action="workshop9/api/city" id="form_city" class="form">
                        <div class="field has-addons">
                            <p class="control">
                                <div class="select">
                                    <select name="city" class="is-rounded has-background-black-bis has-text-light"
                                        id="city">
                                        <option value="">เลือก</option>
                                        <% lists.forEach(function(list){ %>
                                        <option value="<%= list.name %>"><%= list.name %></option>
                                        <% }) %>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                            </p>
                            <div class="field">
                                <p class="control">
                                    <button id="citySubmit" type="submit"
                                        class="button is-inverted is-success has-background-black-bis">
                                        พยากรณ์
                                    </button>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="tile is-child box is-6 has-background-black-ter has-text-light content">
                    <h2 class="has-text-light">จากพิกัดเส้นรุ้งเส้นแวง</h2>
                    <hr>
                    <form action="/workshop9/api/coordinate" id="form_location">
                        <div class="field">
                            <label for="lon">เส้นแวง (Longitude)</label><br>
                            <input name="lon" type="number" step="0.0001"
                                class="input is-rounded has-background-black-bis has-text-light" id="lon"
                                placeholder="0.0000">
                        </div>
                        <div class="field">
                            <label for="lat">เส้นรุ่ง (Latitude)</label>
                            <input name="lat" type="number" step="0.0001"
                                class="input is-rounded has-background-black-bis has-text-light" id="lat"
                                placeholder="0.0000">
                        </div>
                        <div class="is-flex is-justify-content-center">
                            <button type="submit"
                                class="button is-inverted is-success has-background-black-bis">พยากรณ์</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer class="footer has-background-black-bis has-text-light has-text-centered">
        <p>Workshop 9 - แอปพลิเคชันพยากรณ์อากาศ<br>30204-2303 การพัฒนาโปรแกรมบนอุปกรณ์เคลื่อนที่แบบพกพา</p>
        <nav class="level">
            <div class="level-item has-text-centered">
                <div>
                    ดูโค้ดได้ใน <a href="https://github.com/BigzaaGamer/mobileapp_development_hvc2/tree/main/workshop9"
                        target="_blank" ดูโค้ดได้ใน>GitHub</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </footer>
    <script>
        $(window).scroll(function (event) {
            var scroll = $(window).scrollTop();
            if (scroll > 350) {
                $("#workshopName").addClass("slide-in-left");
                $("#workshopName").removeClass("slide-out-left");
                $("#workshopName").removeClass("is-hidden");
            } else {
                $("#workshopName").removeClass("slide-in-left");
                $("#workshopName").addClass("slide-out-left");
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>